name: Intel Core i9-14900KS
description: Intel's current flagship for the desktop market
reviews:
Intel Core i9-14900KS is considered a good processor. 
 Its lower ratings may stem from stability issues found in early 14th and 13th generation models. 
 However, newer revisions have addressed these problems and are now stable.

name: AMD Ryzen 9 9950X3D
description: AMD's current flagship for the desktop market
reviews:
AMD Ryzen 9 9950X3D is widely regarded as a very good processor. 
 According to reviews, it has no major flaws or stability issues.
